 rhythm, shortness of breath, or syncope.', 'Metabolism', 'Pharmacologic response to tetrabenazine should be monitored more closely whenever a potent CYP450 2D6 inhibitor (e.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/170486/', '', 'Oxitriptan, Viloxazine, Vortioxetine, Milnacipran, Tryptophan, Levomilnacipran, Vilazodone', 'Dalfampridine, Tafamidis, Riluzole', 1767369485);
